[ProMED thanks Steve Berger for this background
information. The moderator's comments on the 1st
posting on the subject could be misunderstood,
and it should be made clear that Cryptosporidia
are very resistant to chlorine and are only removed by filtration. - Mod.EP]

[The interactive HealthMap/ProMED map for Sweden is available at:
